    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个没有人能返回的岛屿群……</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9e9218fdd897bd45b165a917ab48497f.poster.avif?t=1769977414\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9e9218fdd897bd45b165a917ab48497f.webm?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9e9218fdd897bd45b165a917ab48497f.mp4?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好进入一个混乱的世界，那里科学实验失败，现实被撕裂。成群的嗜血僵尸、飞行的小鬼、巨大的怪物——这一切已成为曾经繁荣的岛屿上的日常景象。自从一场仍然是谜的灾难发生后，城市陷落，居民变成了恐怖的化身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务简单却致命：收集法术，购买强大的武器，并在探索各类地点的同时摧毁敌人，从哥特式城堡到废弃的实验室。禁用五座防御塔，这些塔形成了通往主岛的屏障。然后，前往异常的震中并摧毁它，同时与一支怪物大军及其巨型领袖作战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Velhodium Isle</strong> 提供 5 个庞大的区域，每个区域都有独特的主题和地点。你将在这里找到：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9f38b7019d4c2a0a6c0b4fa264431b03.poster.avif?t=1769977414\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9f38b7019d4c2a0a6c0b4fa264431b03.webm?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/9f38b7019d4c2a0a6c0b4fa264431b03.mp4?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有骑士和动画树木的中世纪城堡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内部藏有神秘机器人的埃及金字塔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏着危险生物的冰雪荒原和冰冻港口。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满混乱的都市后末日区域。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满鬼魂、恶魔和意外敌人的奇幻世界。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富的游戏玩法：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你通往胜利的道路。你不会抱怨难度——这是一个你可以选择自己游戏风格的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激动人心的复古射击氛围与现代化改进：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实的物理效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全沉浸的光照效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >详细的场景，将你带到不同时代和地点。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Velhodium Isle</strong> 是经典复古 boomer shooter 游戏元素与现代游戏设计相结合的独特作品。拿起你的武器，准备迎接混乱，证明你能在别人无法生存的地方活下来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你能纠正科学家的错误，拯救这个世界吗？</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/5857a6dbdefca8efa59cbb03fcf179a1.poster.avif?t=1769977414\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/5857a6dbdefca8efa59cbb03fcf179a1.webm?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329050/extras/5857a6dbdefca8efa59cbb03fcf179a1.mp4?t=1769977414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
